              <li>‚Ä¢ Feeding instructions</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Training resources</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Microchip registration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">üìã Application Packet</h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Program overview</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Pricing information</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Health testing results</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Contract sample</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Waitlist process</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
